    {
      "title": "Alert Rules Reference",
      "description": "Summary of all 6 alert rules for the Risk Assessment Engine with conditions, severity, and notification channels.",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 69 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## EUDR-028 Risk Assessment Engine Alert Rules\n\n| # | Alert | Condition | Severity | Evaluation | Action |\n|---|-------|-----------|----------|------------|--------|\n| 1 | **High Risk Spike** | high_risk_operators > 20 sustained for 1h | Warning | Every 5m, for 15m | Review high-risk assessments, notify compliance lead |\n| 2 | **Critical Risk Detected** | Any operator classified as critical risk | Critical | Every 1m, for 5m | Page on-call, initiate enhanced due diligence review |\n| 3 | **Assessment Latency** | p99 assessment_duration_seconds > 5s for 10m | Warning | Every 5m, for 10m | Investigate upstream agent latency, check DB performance |\n| 4 | **Unapproved Overrides** | Pending overrides (approved_by IS NULL) > 10 for 24h | Warning | Every 1h, for 24h | Escalate to compliance lead for override approval |\n| 5 | **Benchmark Data Stale** | Country benchmark data > 90 days old | Warning | Every 6h, for 24h | Refresh benchmark data from EU Commission sources |\n| 6 | **System Errors** | API error rate (5xx) > 1% for 5 minutes | Critical | Every 1m, for 5m | Page on-call, check infrastructure and upstream dependencies |\n\n### Notification Channels\n- **Critical**: PagerDuty + Slack #eudr-critical + Email compliance-lead\n- **Warning**: Slack #eudr-alerts + Email on-call\n\n### Runbook Links\n- [Risk Assessment Troubleshooting](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/rae/assessment-troubleshooting)\n- [High Risk Operator Response](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/rae/high-risk-response)\n- [Override Approval Workflow](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/rae/override-approval)\n- [Benchmark Data Refresh](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/rae/benchmark-refresh)\n- [Article 10 Criteria Failure Investigation](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/rae/article10-investigation)\n- [Performance Degradation](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/rae/perf-degradation)"
      }
    }
